paragraphs.text:
%hive
select substr(tran_dt, 0,10) as tran_date,sum(tran_amt) as sum_tran_amt, count(tran_dt) as ct_tran from transactions_aml
group by substr(tran_dt, 0,10)
order by tran_date

%hive
select count(*) as ct_tran from transactions_aml
